# Gradient Descent

This folder contains simple explanations and implementations of **Gradient Descent**, a core optimization algorithm used in Machine Learning.

---

## What is Gradient Descent?

Gradient Descent is an iterative method used to **minimize a loss function** by updating model parameters in the direction of the negative gradient.

---

